@Autowired
private RedisTemplate redisTemplate;

@Autowired
private JmsTemplate jmsTemplate;

@Autowired
private Destination destination;

@Override
public void createSmsCode(String phone) throws Exception {
    //çæ4ä½ä»¥åéæºæ°
    String code =  (int) (Math.random()*1000)+"";
    System.out.println("éªè¯ç ï¼"+code);
    //å­å¥ç¼å­
    redisTemplate.boundHashOps("smscode").put(phone, code);

    //åéæ¶æ¯å°MQ
    sendMsg(phone,code);
}

@Value("${template_code}")
private String template_code;

@Value("${sign_name}")
private String sign_name;


/***
 * åéæ¶æ¯
 */
public void sendMsg(final String phone,final String code) throws Exception{
    //æ¶æ¯åé
    jmsTemplate.send(destination, new MessageCreator() {
        @Override
        public Message createMessage(Session session) throws JMSException {
            MapMessage mapMessage = session.createMapMessage();
            mapMessage.setString("templateCode",template_code);
            mapMessage.setString("signName",sign_name);
            mapMessage.setString("mobile",phone);

            Map<String,String> parameter = new HashMap<String,String>();
            parameter.put("code",code);
            mapMessage.setString("param", JSON.toJSONString(parameter));
            return mapMessage;
        }
    });
}

public boolean checkSmsCode(String phone, String code) {
    //å¾å°ç¼å­ä¸­å­å¨çéªè¯ç 
    String sysCode = (String) redisTemplate.boundHashOps("smscode").get(phone);

    }

}
